ENERGY
This program is base on nova architecture 
It's used to dispatch and migration virtual machine

energy-api privode some restful api to web ui

energy-sampler will sample some machine information
       libvirt sample virtual machine information
       ipmi  sample some machine information and control computer power

energy-server will load some manager which can control openstack, hadoop and so on.
openstack manager will control vm migration and computer power
it's a thrift server and run some periodism task

energy-agent is a agent to request server.
